      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing. a shell doesn't have worth. it's just empty. there's no point in \"moving on\" when there's nothing left to move with. the version of me that actually achieved things, that people respected... that person is gone for good. it's like i'm already a ghost haunting my own life.",
